{"tid":1781337,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"PS4獨佔動作遊戲《Ghost of Tsushima》全新預告釋出，預定2020年夏季推出！","createTime":"2019-12-13T05:36:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-17T05:17:37.000Z","uid":1886,"like":5,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"9cae7c5fd31ebf8e448f6b49f67bd83f64d0c0e0","tid":1781337,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-13T05:36:03.000Z","msg":"由索尼互動娛樂全球工作室旗下的Sucker Punch Productions 開發， PS4 獨佔新作動作冒險遊戲《對馬幽魂》(Ghost of Tsushima)在稍早的遊戲大獎 The Game Awards 2019 典禮上，公布了長達四分鐘正式宣傳預告，包括更多劇情演出及遊玩畫面，同時公開預定發售日期，將於 2020 年夏季推出。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://pgw.udn.com.tw/gw/photo.php?u=https://uc.udn.com.tw/photo/2019/12/13/99/7190235.png&amp;x=0&amp;y=0&amp;sw=0&amp;sh=0&amp;sl=W&amp;fw=1050\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpgw.udn.com.tw%2Fgw%2Fphoto.php%3Fu%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fuc.udn.com.tw%2Fphoto%2F2019%2F12%2F13%2F99%2F7190235.png%26x%3D0%26y%3D0%26sw%3D0%26sh%3D0%26sl%3DW%26fw%3D1050&h=f5bc433e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n《對馬幽魂》背景設定在日本封建時代的1274年，約為蒙古入侵日本的時間，玩家扮演世居對馬島的武士一族的「Ghost」武士境井仁，為了抵禦外敵入侵，而踏上戰途。遊戲採開放世界，預告中刻意剪輯了許多騎馬場景，顯示可探索區域的廣大。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://pgw.udn.com.tw/gw/photo.php?u=https://uc.udn.com.tw/photo/2019/12/13/99/7190233.png&amp;x=0&amp;y=0&amp;sw=0&amp;sh=0&amp;sl=W&amp;fw=1050\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpgw.udn.com.tw%2Fgw%2Fphoto.php%3Fu%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fuc.udn.com.tw%2Fphoto%2F2019%2F12%2F13%2F99%2F7190233.png%26x%3D0%26y%3D0%26sw%3D0%26sh%3D0%26sl%3DW%26fw%3D1050&h=89fb7c89&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://pgw.udn.com.tw/gw/photo.php?u=https://uc.udn.com.tw/photo/2019/12/13/99/7190237.png&amp;x=0&amp;y=0&amp;sw=0&amp;sh=0&amp;sl=W&amp;fw=1050\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpgw.udn.com.tw%2Fgw%2Fphoto.php%3Fu%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fuc.udn.com.tw%2Fphoto%2F2019%2F12%2F13%2F99%2F7190237.png%26x%3D0%26y%3D0%26sw%3D0%26sh%3D0%26sl%3DW%26fw%3D1050&h=68ae546c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\